CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, May 11, 1957, pg. 10 reads: "AKA Debs - Preparing to make their bow Penn-Sheraton Hotel, May 18, under the auspices of Alpha Kappa Alpha sorority, are these charming young ladies... Judy Loften, Alice Weatherly, Sara Blakely, Adrienne Phillips, and Judy Matthews..."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of 1957 Alpha Kappa Alpha Debutantes including Judy Loftin, second from left, Alice Weatherly, holding shoe, and Sara Blakely, second from right, standing in interior
